caption: A train horn blows as a train approaches with warning bells ringing
A bird tweets far away and someone flushes the toilet
Metal scrapping on wood followed by wood sanding then more metal scrapping against wood
Heavy wind followed by yelling and cheering
A speech and gunfire followed by a gun being loaded
A dog whimpering followed by a dog growling and barking as metal jingles and footsteps squeak on hard surface
Echoing male speech, laughter and applause
